videos.headline: Furman's Abrams pushes pile for the TD
videos.description: Devin Abrams pushes the pile into the end zone giving Furman an early 7-3 lead vs. Virginia Tech.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Furman's Abrams pushes pile for the TD) 2019/09/14

videos.headline: Furman QB Grainger scrambles 15-yards for the TD
videos.description: Furman quarterback Darren Grainger avoids the pass rush then scrambles into the end zone for the 15-yard touchdown vs. Virginia Tech.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Furman QB Grainger scrambles 15-yards for the TD) 2019/09/14

videos.headline: King's big run leads to Hokies TD
videos.description: Virginia Tech running back Keshawn King goes 54 yards to the Furman 14, then a few plays later Hokies' tight end James Mitchell finds the end zone from 3-yards out.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_Highlight (King's big run leads to Hokies TD) 2019/09/14
